{"tid":2122101,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"傷口 掂到都唔痛 先係真痊癒","createTime":"2020-07-23T18:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T21:44:26.000Z","uid":247521,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"adbc587049377c6fe2699d31d55205e401485e86","tid":2122101,"uid":247521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T18:51:44.000Z","msg":"我愈強迫自己向前 <br />\n個心就愈黎愈痛 <br />\n<br />\n幾時先可以做到電影中句對白既境界"},{"pid":"172cf98d7ba51db7fb4e98853d10ec0a9b96e28c","tid":2122101,"uid":164393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T18:56:20.000Z","msg":"越逼自己忘記 同時都係提醒緊自己記住<br />\n順其自然啦"},{"pid":"ca139196e2e223debb22a25c769c2b2bb19bde7a","tid":2122101,"uid":206986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adbc587049377c6fe2699d31d55205e401485e86","tid":2122101,"uid":247521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T18:51:44.000Z","msg":"我愈強迫自己向前 <br />\n個心就愈黎愈痛 <br />\n<br />\n幾時先可以做到電影中句對白既境界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T18:56:28.000Z","msg":"共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a267a4435224a119d2bb02c7dda57751457ac06d","tid":2122101,"uid":229169,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T19:17:37.000Z","msg":"首先，唔好強迫自己向前<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩情緒就盡情發洩出來<br />\n想同fd呻就呻，想出街玩就玩，想頹就頹，想諗起啲美好回憶就諗<br />\n發洩到一個地步就自然會有：我唔可以再咁落去啦 嘅念頭<br />\n到時自然會慢慢好轉（唔識講咩狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之唔好迫自己短時間放低<br />\n你諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同對方建立感情要好長時間，仲花咗咁多心機經營<br />\n同對方嘅回憶邊有可能話放低就放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你愈壓抑，啲美好回億愈係出現喺你面前<br />\n逃避，並唔係放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油 <br />\n雖然好難捱，但你會變得比你想像中堅強㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">當初分手好突然<br />\n開頭強迫自己冇事<br />\n但眼淚都係自己流落來<br />\n但鬱到個心好酸<br />\n之後索性發洩晒出來<br />\n煩住朋友就煩 喊就喊<br />\n喊到一個地步就諗通左</span>"},{"pid":"f5bbe82dcf549b331293acbcaf0ac6473ee8e676","tid":2122101,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T19:35:15.000Z","msg":"都過咗幾年，每當聽到對方嘅消息，都仲係會有啲唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66235bb128bd7ad82c675cd00ca5719a7ae2022","tid":2122101,"uid":71576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5bbe82dcf549b331293acbcaf0ac6473ee8e676","tid":2122101,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T19:35:15.000Z","msg":"都過咗幾年，每當聽到對方嘅消息，都仲係會有啲唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T20:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵返個陳樂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739f034141ffe15f551e46076db5738899501eba","tid":2122101,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d66235bb128bd7ad82c675cd00ca5719a7ae2022","tid":2122101,"uid":71576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5bbe82dcf549b331293acbcaf0ac6473ee8e676","tid":2122101,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T19:35:15.000Z","msg":"都過咗幾年，每當聽到對方嘅消息，都仲係會有啲唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T20:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵返個陳樂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T20:19:40.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1559670ca341320647ab6c99d909aa036c5c8a17","tid":2122101,"uid":71576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"739f034141ffe15f551e46076db5738