\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，多謝你聽我9up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:15:29.000Z","msg":"大家手腳 明既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n及早放下 等個維修佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早啲休息"},{"pid":"ee0ea77165665e83bb469deeecde9ed40f99bddb","tid":2122101,"uid":247521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5bbe82dcf549b331293acbcaf0ac6473ee8e676","tid":2122101,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T19:35:15.000Z","msg":"都過咗幾年，每當聽到對方嘅消息，都仲係會有啲唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:16:23.000Z","msg":"又係你阿 程嘉藍 <br />\n係有啲唔開心 但分開左人地過得好與唔好 都己經與自己無關...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日都諗我都可以佢現家身邊啲人咁陪佢 <br />\n<br />\n這些我都做得到 但那個人己經不是我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad8a7618c7b0db585650835994b28fef7f712f8","tid":2122101,"uid":247521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a267a4435224a119d2bb02c7dda57751457ac06d","tid":2122101,"uid":229169,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T19:17:37.000Z","msg":"首先，唔好強迫自己向前<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩情緒就盡情發洩出來<br />\n想同fd呻就呻，想出街玩就玩，想頹就頹，想諗起啲美好回憶就諗<br />\n發洩到一個地步就自然會有：我唔可以再咁落去啦 嘅念頭<br />\n到時自然會慢慢好轉（唔識講咩狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之唔好迫自己短時間放低<br />\n你諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同對方建立感情要好長時間，仲花咗咁多心機經營<br />\n同對方嘅回憶邊有可能話放低就放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你愈壓抑，啲美好回億愈係出現喺你面前<br />\n逃避，並唔係放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油 <br />\n雖然好難捱，但你會變得比你想像中堅強㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">當初分手好突然<br />\n開頭強迫自己冇事<br />\n但眼淚都係自己流落來<br />\n但鬱到個心好酸<br />\n之後索性發洩晒出來<br />\n煩住朋友就煩 喊就喊<br />\n喊到一個地步就諗通左</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:21:33.000Z","msg":"我都係突然之間...<br />\n諗下諗下自己眼濕濕 <br />\n但見到人地己經好開心<br />\n自己仲原地打轉<br />\n一聽到一睇到<br />\n就一陣心痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲朋友己經信唔過<br />\n或者己經唔會係朋友"},{"pid":"9aa6065d57299603a1bd3cf4d0ad1512e6e01e25","tid":2122101,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aaa582dc80c37be91b6da2e4060504193326263","tid":2122101,"uid":71576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c5d3ca16ddef6411b5d3bfd9c8182acb97bf9c6","tid":2122101,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eeb9ba046b581a125d3584bd4c50c6b7ef6ead6","tid":2122101,"uid":71576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:03:17.000Z","msg":"人就係咁犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔值得 何苦呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:08:21.000Z","msg":"其實都好過之前好多，不過無啦啦又有舊同學提起佢啲野，真係好唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有對象可能會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，多謝你聽我9up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:15:29.000Z","msg":"大家手腳 明既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n及早放下 等個維修佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早啲休息"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:22:11.000Z","msg":"等緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，愛你"},{"pid":"7dd4257b22928ea63ed6f9a3c5b721459ba476cb","tid":2122101,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee0ea77165665e83bb469deeecde9ed40f99bddb","tid":2122101,"uid":247521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5bbe82dcf549b331293ac